    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Three validation activities (bench hemolysis, PIV velocity, H-Q curve) provide corroborating evidence across independent QoIs. Discretization error GCI of 3.2% satisfies the 5% threshold. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
